# The ROOT AGENTS.md is a SHARED, committed operating standard for this repo. The
# user's global gitignore (~/.config/git/ignore) ignores AGENTS.md everywhere;
# this negation re-includes ONLY the root one so the team gets it. (CLAUDE.md
# stays local; upstream/AGENTS.md stays ignored — upstream is vendored, untracked.)
!/AGENTS.md
